  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/40ffdbfbf0a1af6c9a887b99dd821f78.avif?t=1772926834\" width=616 height=128 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/31eecc2e4b1f4f4ff4d1114606ed0029.apng?t=1772926834\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/31eecc2e4b1f4f4ff4d1114606ed0029.poster.avif?t=1772926834\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=72 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Forest of Worlds is withering, and along with it; the creative spark of every living thing. Venture into fantastical levels, gather the <strong>Golden Leaves</strong> within, and use them to avert the fate of a world devoid of imagination!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/884cdaab78ac9bd31456663ebbf3a4e9.poster.avif?t=1772926834\" width=614 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/884cdaab78ac9bd31456663ebbf3a4e9.webm?t=1772926834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/3cf2d5cac1b26969099424efcec0ab60.poster.avif?t=1772926834\" width=614 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/3cf2d5cac1b26969099424efcec0ab60.webm?t=1772926834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/3cf2d5cac1b26969099424efcec0ab60.mp4?t=1772926834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/86b6c6efaab61145194fea91dd9e913e.webp?t=1772926834\" width=30 height=20 /></span>Tackle 66 finely-tuned screens built for newcomers and speed-runners alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/ff0ef1de31f25949a69cd61d1258f19f.webp?t=1772926834\" width=30 height=20 /></span>Collect Crystal Berries by clearing levels quickly to unlock <strong>Bonus Levels</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/09a4597e11bf19564fc5c27e089e66cb.webp?t=1772926834\" width=30 height=20 /></span>Race for the World Record using a dedicated <strong>Speedrun Mode</strong> to display an in-game timer, speed up level transitions, and auto-skip dialogue sequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/6d8bb28723d5952a1d6b32d80899955b.webp?t=1772926834\" width=30 height=20 /></span>Generous checkpoints and a co-operative <strong>Assist Mode</strong> help players of all ages and ability see everything the game has to offer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/b905d89c415f10686c7c657d22d0f8af.webp?t=1772926834\" width=30 height=20 /></span>Unlock <strong>Shuffle Mode</strong> to randomize level connections and Leaf positions. Share seeds and race friends, or try to top the leaderboard of the <strong>Daily Challenge</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/4ed135dfce974e61e7fb0925f4b5b946.poster.avif?t=1772926834\" width=614 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/4ed135dfce974e61e7fb0925f4b5b946.webm?t=1772926834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/57933eac61e22fe112afe15b10d07f5f.webp?t=1772926834\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/57933eac61e22fe112afe15b10d07f5f.poster.avif?t=1772926834\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=72 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unless also includes the following accessibility features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjustable Game Speed </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable Inputs </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tweak jump and wall-cling behaviour </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Font selection and Text scaling </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High contrast UI & reduced distraction modes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/6eb4a1b549c911a8d33d90a4df7f590b.poster.avif?t=1772926834\" width=614 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/6eb4a1b549c911a8d33d90a4df7f590b.webm?t=1772926834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/bc73bac121891e926840fb86c4a23fa9.apng?t=1772926834\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/bc73bac121891e926840fb86c4a23fa9.poster.avif?t=1772926834\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=72 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discuss the game, share record-breaking runs, and be the first to get news on the development of Unless! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JOIN OUR DISCORD</strong> via the invite link in the right sidebar.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/c559eaf8d4d961957ca15e6f4f379dbe.poster.avif?t=1772926834\" width=614 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944340/extras/c559eaf8d4d961957ca15e6f4f379dbe.webm?t=1772926834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
